Localization.Name: Vacha Jacket Mahogany
Localization.Description: Carrying Capacity: 400 µSCU\n\nThe Vacha jacket offers the wearer an admirable degree of comfort across a wide range of environments thanks to its sealed cuffs and utility neck collar. Additionally, the rugged design features a sealed cross closure, incorporated belt, and auxiliary ports. The garment's sheer durability and utility has cemented the Vacha jacket as a perennial favorite in Habidash's collection.
